<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201106/d1b5710dc98d48668ac5095817bc95d2.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">甘肃顺丰江淮帅铃交车仪式</span></img></p>
